commentary: Mashrafe Mortaza to Ramdin, no run is that something? The umpires convene to discuss. Has Ramdin gloved behind? Has it carried to the keeper? Another slower ball from Mortaza, but this time seemed to bounce a touch more than the batsman expected. commentary: Rampaul to Mashrafe Mortaza, 1 run up in the blockhole as Sohag gets some willow on it before setting off for a quick single as the ball rolls to the off side. The throw coming in manages to hit the stumps at the non-striker's, but his bat didn't come down in time, and he would have been given out if someone had appealed, but no one appealed, and that is a lesson learned young'uns . Mortaza fortunate to get away with that one
